.SH NAME
.PP
\f[B]config\f[] \[en] get information about Virgil CLI configuration
file.
.SH SYNOPSIS
.IP
.nf
\f[C]
\ \ \ \ virgil\ config\ \ [\-o\ <file>]\ [\-g]\ [\-l]\ [\-t]\ [\-\-]\ [\-\-version]\ [\-h]
